content: Before we begin, I'd like to remind you that our comments and responses to your questions on the management's view as of today only and will include statements related to our financial outlook for both the third quarter and full year 2022 and the assumptions and drivers underlying such guidance, including the impact of our sales season, client launches and our expected utilization rate and mix, our anticipated number of clients in covered lives for 2023, the impact of COVID-19 including variants, on our business, clients, member activity and industry operations, the impact of any shortages or disruptions in the pharmacy medication supply chain on our business and our financial condition, our ability to acquire new clients and retain and upsell existing clients; our market opportunity, size and expectation of long-term growth our plans for the expansion of our business, including expansion into other markets and services offered, our business performance, industry outlook, strategy, future investments, plans and objectives, which are forward-looking statements under the federal securities laws.
